item.title: CVE-2023-35850|2024-09-25T15:45:21.497Z -- sunnet -- wmpro
item.description: SUNNET WMPro portal's file management function has a vulnerability of insufficient filtering for user input. A remote attacker with administrator privilege or a privileged account can exploit this vulnerability to inject and execute arbitrary system commands to perform arbitrary system operations or disrupt service.

item.title: CVE-2023-35851|2024-09-25T15:44:38.562Z -- sunnet -- wmpro
item.description: SUNNET WMPro portal's FAQ function has insufficient validation for user input. An unauthenticated remote attacker can inject arbitrary SQL commands to obtain sensitive information via a database.
